aiXcoder.configuration.endpoint: Specifies the endpoint for code suggestion server.
aiXcoder.configuration.selfLearning: ([Professional Edition](https://www.aixcoder.com/#/Product?tab=0)) Allows aiXcoder to learn your coding idiom.
aiXcoder.configuration.searchEndpoint: Specifies the endpoint for code search server.
aiXcoder.configuration.searchIntegratedW: Whether to use integrated webview for code search or not.
aiXcoder.configuration.searchDefaultBrow: Specifies the default browser executable, launched like <browser_executable> <url>. It is also possible to specify additional arguments, E.g. `%ProgramFiles%\Mozilla Firefox\firefox.exe -new-tab`. Default: default browser from OS.
aiXcoder.configuration.enableTelemetry: Send anonoymous usage data and errors to aiXcoder telemetry service.
aiXcoder.configuration.additionalParamet: (Only for advanced usages) URL encoded params.
aiXcoder.configuration.alwaysTrigger: If set to true, aiXcoder suggestions are always triggered as you type. Otherwise, it only triggers explictly with e.g. `Ctrl+Space`.
aiXcoder.configuration.autoImport: Automatically import missing packages in completions.
aiXcoder.configuration.sortOnly: No long completion, only sorts the completions (will decrease delay).
aiXcoder.configuration.longResultRank: The prefered rank of long completion result.
aiXcoder.configuration.symbol: The symbol used to mark aiXcoder predictions
aiXcoder.command.resetMessages.title: Reset messages
aiXcoder.command.search.title: Search with aiXcoder...
aiXcoder.configuration.localShowIncomple: Show incomplete suggestions before indexing finishes
